sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Training Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Master as Master Pod<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Worker as Worker Pod(s)<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Storage as Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: Training Job Creation and Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>Informer (in-cluster)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: GET PyTorchJob<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: POST create master pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: POST create worker pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: POST create service<br/>port 23456/TCP
    Operator->>K8sAPI: PATCH job status<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 2: Distributed Training Communication (PyTorch)

    Worker->>Master: Connect for coordination<br/>TCP/23456<br/>No encryption
    Master->>Worker: Distribute gradients<br/>TCP/23456<br/>No encryption
    Worker->>Storage: Download dataset<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Job credentials
    Storage-->>Worker: Training data
    Master->>Storage: Save checkpoints<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Job credentials
    Storage-->>Master: Checkpoint saved

    Worker->>K8sAPI: Update pod status<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch pod status<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: PATCH job status: Succeeded<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prom->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>No auth
    Operator-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>Operator telemetry

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 4: Health Checks

    K8sAPI->>Operator: GET /healthz<br/>HTTP/8081
    Operator-->>K8sAPI: 200 OK
    K8sAPI->>Operator: GET /readyz<br/>HTTP/8081
    Operator-->>K8sAPI: 200 OK
